/li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n<b>Year 59 After the Conquest</b> (<b>59 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 59th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>59 AC was the first of a two-year exceptionally cold and cruel winter. Crops failed in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. The price of bread and meat rose, and there was famine. The most terrible adversity was the widespread of the winter plague known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivers\" title=\"Shivers\">Shivers</a>, which caused the deaths of thousands of people throughout <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, including two great lords, two members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a>, and two members of the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=59_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><b>In King's Landing</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Samgood_of_Sour_Hill\" title=\"Samgood of Sour Hill\">Samgood of Sour Hill</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Victor_the_Valiant\" title=\"Victor the Valiant\">Victor the Valiant</a> of the Kingsguard dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Albin_Massey\" title=\"Albin Massey\">Albin Massey</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rego_Draz\" title=\"Rego Draz\">Rego Draz</a>, murdered by a mob.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_Corbray\" title=\"Qarl Corbray\">Qarl Corbray</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Benifer\" title=\"Benifer\">Benifer</a> dies from the Shivers.</li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Crownlands</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edwell_Celtigar\" title=\"Edwell Celtigar\">Edwell Celtigar</a> and his son and heir die from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\">Staunton</a>, his wife, and their children die from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Edyth\" title=\"Edyth\">Edyth</a> dies from the Shivers on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Velaryon_(son_of_Aethan)\" title=\"Daemon Velaryon (son of Aethan)\">Daemon Velaryon</a>'s second son and three of his daughters dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\">Bar Emmon</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rosby\" title=\"House Rosby\">Rosby</a> dies from the Shivers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>In Oldtown</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>A quarter of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>'s population dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>The wife and children of <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Hightower\" title=\"Eustace Hightower\">Eustace Hightower</a> die from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Hightower\" title=\"Donnel Hightower\">Donnel Hightower</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Twoscore of the <a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a> die from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>A third of the <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaesters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaesters\">archmaesters</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maesters</a>, acolytes and the novices at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> die from the Shivers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Riverlands</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Prentys_Tully\" title=\"Prentys Tully\">Prentys Tully</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lucinda_Tully\" title=\"Lucinda Tully\">Lucinda Tully</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lady Jirelle of <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> dies from the Shivers.</li></ul>\n<p><b>In the Westerlands</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Lannister\" title=\"Lyman Lannister\">Lyman Lannister</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Marbrand\" title=\"House Marbrand\">Marbrand</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarbeck\" title=\"House Tarbeck\">Tarbeck</a> dies from the Shivers.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">Westerling</a> dies from the Shivers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=59_AC&amp;action=edi